{"tid":1498919,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「獅子山下 」羅文黃霑顧嘉煇攜手鼓勵香港人","createTime":"2019-08-23T14:24:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-23T16:27:49.000Z","uid":157404,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"e1509594f8195e4344dbbfff3c3e0ab4b30dc476","tid":1498919,"uid":157404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T14:24:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/S0AR1ao.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FS0AR1ao.jpg&h=475be63d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n首先多謝巴打影咗張咁靚咁感動嘅相<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/s61E98A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fs61E98A.jpg&h=a887d639&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n然後想分享一吓細細個就聽嘅歌<br />\n嗰時只係覺得順口易記跟住唱<br />\n今日見到獅子山人鏈搵返嚟聽<br />\n<br />\n羅文 <br />\n<br />\n獅子山下<br />\n<br />\n作詞：黃霑<br />\n作曲：顧嘉煇<br />\n編曲：顧嘉煇<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">人生中有歡喜 難免亦常有淚<br />\n我哋大家 在獅子山下相遇上<br />\n總算是歡笑多於唏噓</span><br />\n<br />\n人生不免崎嶇 難以絕無掛慮<br />\n既是同舟 在獅子山下且共濟<br />\n拋棄區分求共對<br />\n<br />\n放開彼此心中矛盾 理想一起去追<br />\n同舟人 誓相隨 無畏更無懼<br />\n<br />\n同處海角天邊 攜手踏平崎嶇<br />\n我哋大家 用艱辛努力寫下那<br />\n不朽香江名句<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>放開彼此心中矛盾 理想一起去追<br />\n同舟人 誓相隨 無畏更無懼</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">同處海角天邊 攜手踏平崎嶇</span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">我哋大家 用艱辛努力寫下那<br />\n不朽香江名句</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n每字每句都唱到入心坎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我真係好愛香港更愛香港人<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">多謝大家一齊創造每一個奇蹟</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港，時代革命。</span>"},{"pid":"efd764f144dee53e38b9409975dd1b83ecff207b","tid":1498919,"uid":227303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T14:27:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可"},{"pid":"4b99f8692c9759054326bd3fa06f7d982bb2d562","tid":1498919,"uid":2923,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T14:28:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c8f3160097955ac91f40a0b71d9fae8e7375b3c","tid":1498919,"uid":114429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T14:28:40.000Z","msg":"香港人   加油!"},{"pid":"e3a53ad0e0f8390368574b32afb8c776b7d53ee6","tid":1498919,"uid":146724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T15:21:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 五大訴求 爭取到底 缺一不可"},{"pid":"f508edb195eb8186be1bc5193dd5ea810e8f2e87","tid":1498919,"uid":50457,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T15:24:41.000Z","msg":"上一代：獅子山下精神<br />\n這一代：獅子山上精神"},{"pid":"0448a8615577b1ddcd4948d49c06c1f724f89df2","tid":1498919,"uid":289115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"efd764f144dee53e38b9409975dd1b83ecff207b","tid":1498919,"uid":227303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T14:27:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T15:30:32.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"6755f8ef1935bf7714208c9939024978f2699fa6","tid":1498919,"uid":273585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T16:27:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgm